property.name: query
property.value: "SELECT {actions:PK} action, {actions:activated} activated, {actions:comment} actioncomment, {workflows:PK} workflow FROM {WORKFLOWACTION AS actions}, {Workflow AS workflows} WHERE {actions:workflow} = {workflows:PK} AND {actions:status} = ?status AND ({actions:principalAssigned} = ?session.user OR {actions:principalAssigned} IN (?session.user.allgroups)) AND {actions:template} IN (?template) ORDER BY workflow, action"
